law.history: Repealed 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 301, subtit. 99, sec. 3, effective June 18, 1970. -- Created 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 1, effective September 1, 1950.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Kinds of insurance and insurers to which KRS 304.625 to 304.644 apply; coverage by other laws; designation as to which law to apply.
